

Ques- Write a Python program to import "crop.csv" and do the following task-
1.) Draw scatter plot- We have data on the yield and rainfall for different crops in  regions)
2.) Draw a histogram to visualize the distribution of crop ages.
3.) Draw a line plot to visualize the trend in crop yield for each crop.


import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

df = pd.read_csv('crop2.csv')

plt.scatter(df['Rainfall'], df['Yield'],color='red',marker='o',s=10)
plt.xlabel('Rainfall')
plt.ylabel('Yield')
plt.title('Visualizing rainfall and yield throught scatter plot  ')
plt.show()

plt.hist(df['Age'],color='green')
plt.xlabel('Age')
plt.ylabel('Frequency')
plt.title('Visualizing distribution of crop ages using histogram')
plt.show()

for crop, crop_df in df.groupby('Crop'):
    plt.plot(crop_df['Year'], crop_df['Yield'], label=crop,marker='o')
plt.xlabel('Year')
plt.ylabel('Yield')
plt.title('Visualizing Trend in Crop Yield Over Time using line plot')
plt.legend()
plt.show()

